[32m│[0m **Severity**: HIGH                                                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Description**: The `is_admin` parameter in the profile update form can be manipulated to grant admin privileges.                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Evidence**:                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```bash                                                                                                                                              [32m│[0m
