[32m│[0m ## 🔐 AUTHORIZATION FLAWS                                                                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Missing Authorization Checks**:                                                                                                                [32m│[0m
