[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Proper Authorization Should**:                                                                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Validate `company_id` matches JWT `sub` claim                                                                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Restrict `is_admin` modification to super-admin only                                                                                              [32m│[0m
